{"tid":875437,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(å¤§é™¸å¯Œè±ª) ç‹å¥æ—å…¬å¸æ‹æ” ã€Šæˆ‘çš„è‹±é›„å­¸é™¢ã€‹çœŸäººé›»å½±ç‰ˆ","createTime":"2018-10-25T01:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T09:46:38.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6c4ad588b114f0e375f31dcbbf44cbbbf9c0c1","tid":875437,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T01:53:07.000Z","msg":"å¤§é™¸å¯Œè±ªç‹å¥æ—æ——ä¸‹å…¬å¸Legendaryæœƒå°‡æ—¥æœ¬å‹•æ¼«ã€Šæˆ‘çš„è‹±é›„å­¸é™¢ã€‹æ”¹ç¯‡ç‚ºçœŸäººé›»å½±. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://deadline.com/2018/10/my-hero-academia-movie-live-action-legendary-detective-pikachu-1202488986/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fmy-hero-academia-movie-live-action-legendary-detective-pikachu-1202488986%2F&d=HlapleOAzD3wBg705ZUsmHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=a6bcfd9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://deadline.com/2018/10/my-hero-academia-movie-live-action-legendary-detective-pikachu-1202488986/</a><br />\n<br />\nLegendary To Adapt Manga &lsquo;My Hero Academia&rsquo; Into Live-Action Movie<br />\nby Patrick Hipes<br />\nand Geoff Boucher<br />\nOctober 24, 2018 4:25pm<br />\n<br />\nLegendary said Wednesday it plans to adapt Kohei Horikoshi&rsquo;s manga franchise My Hero Academia into a live-action feature film. It joins a slate at the company that includes the feature film Detective Pikachu based on the Pokemon franchise.<br />\n<br />\nThe manga version of the series, written and illustrated by Horikoshi, launched in 2014 and a year later was adapted in anime form. It centers on Izuku, a young boy who daydreams about being a hero but is clearly not a likely candidate &mdash; that&rsquo;s because he lives in a world where four out of every five people have a superpower (called a &ldquo;quirk&rdquo; ability) which means an &ldquo;average&rdquo; kid is nether common nor close to average. Izuku defies the odds and enroll in one of the world&rsquo;s most prestigious and intimidating hero academies where he will find challenges that require him to risk everything to prove himself to be truly special.<br />\n<br />\nThe plot of a common kid struggling for acceptance in a fantastical campus setting has some hallmarks in common with the family-friendly comedy Sky High (2005) and also brings to mind Hermione Granger&rsquo;s plight at Hogwarts in the Harry Potter mythology.<br />\n<br />\nAn animated film, My Hero Academia: Two Heroes, bowed earlier this month in the U.S. via Funimation Films.<br />\n<br />\nThe anime series is so popular in Japan that it was incorporated into a tandem advertising campaign there with Avengers: Infinity War in the months leading up to the the show&rsquo;s third seasons and the film&rsquo;s release in the territory, both in April. The collaboration between Disney and JNN/Bones Inc presented the properties on equal footing in posters, postcards and products.<br />\n<br />\nThe property took on life in a third medium with popular video game adaptations, first in 2016 (for Nintendo 3DS) and then this year (for PlayStation 4, Xbox One).<br />\n<br />\nAlex Garcia and Jay Ashenfelter will oversee the live-action project on behalf of Legendary, with Ryosuke Yoritomi on behalf of the manga publisher Shueisha. Toho will distribute the film in Japan.<br />\n<br />\nDetective Pikachu, which stars Ryan Reynolds and Ken Watanabe, has a May 10, 2019 release date via Warner Bros. The pic is part of Legendary&rsquo;s pending move from its current home at Universal back to Warner Bros; Legendary is not reupping its Uni deal, instead eyeing a six-picture, non-exclusive co-financing and releasing pact at WB."},{"pid":"7b0a573eeed93aa5ce3f50a1ea843a4b45ec2b4d","tid":875437,"uid":150609,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:26:25.000Z","msg":"å· åŠ›<br />\n<br />\næµå³äº¦å‡¡åšä¸»è§’å°±ğŸ¤™ğŸ»"},{"pid":"1874a29c3a2216f7496c0fdc0efb5345141e38de","tid":875437,"uid":31637,"like":10,"dislike